{
  "stem": "25651.13",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One of those mornings we stop, and a farmer is going over one of these humpbacked bridges over the railway.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he, he asks us who we are, you see?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we said, we are Jews from Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Auschwitz is in Silesia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Where are we?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we were still in Silesia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he named a place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] So they asked him for some food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he said, I've got nothing on me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Anyway, I wouldn't give it to Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] You know, and he said something, you're all guilty.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That's why we've put you into camps.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "What did he mean?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was a German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know what he meant.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Catholic guilt.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It wasn't a discussion.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was sort of, he was on the bridge, we were in the wagon underneath.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they put me in front and said, look.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There's a kid.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Is he guilty of anything?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So he says, well, he must have done something if German justice put him into prison.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And whilst we were talking, two men jumped out and they jumped him, dragged him back into the train, took his clothes and his papers that he had on him, and they disappeared.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And he was dressed in these rags amongst us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said, wait till I tell them, you know, at the next station.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we arrive at the station, and he goes to a German guard, and he talks to him in German.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he says, you know, I'm a German.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm not with these Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the German looks at him and takes his rifle butt and gives him one with the rifle butt, the way he would do to a Jewish prisoner.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
